body_html: Thanks for reaching out @namrathaurs. The TensorFlow team is committed to supporting Ubuntu Linux 14 LTE to 16. Ubuntu 12.04 isn't in our support matrix. That release is actually going to be EOL in two months. The Ubuntu team is going to stop creating security updates for your system. Please consider upgrading as soon as possible.
